    <p>A <i>schema annotation</i> is a documentation snippet associated with the definition of an
      element or attribute in a schema. If such a schema is associated with an XML document, the
      annotations are displayed in the <xref keyref="glossentry_content-completion-assistant"
          ><term>Content Completion Assistant</term></xref>.</p>
